{"metadata":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"itemsChanged","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Case","title":"MenuModelSignalName.itemsChanged","symbolKind":"case","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"externalID":"s:3GIO19MenuModelSignalNameO12itemsChangedyA2CmF"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MenuModelSignalName"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"text":"Emitted when a change has occurred to the menu.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MenuModelSignalName\/itemsChanged"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"itemsChanged"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The only changes that can occur to a menu is that items are removed","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"or added.  Items may not change (except by being removed and added"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"back in the same location).  This signal is capable of describing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"both of those changes (at the same time)."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The signal means that starting at the index "},{"code":"position","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"removed","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"items were removed and ","type":"text"},{"code":"added","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" items were added in their place.  If","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"removed","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is zero then only items were added.  If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"added"},{"type":"text","text":" is zero"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"then only items were removed."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"As an example, if the menu contains items a, b, c, d (in that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"order) and the signal (2, 1, 3) occurs then the new composition of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the menu will be a, b, _, _, _, d (with each _ representing some"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"new item)."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Signal handlers may query the model (particularly the added items)","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and expect to see the results of the modification that is being"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"reported.  The signal is emitted after the modification.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/menumodelsignalname\/itemschanged"]}],"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/MenuModelSignalName/itemsChanged":{"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MenuModelSignalName\/itemsChanged","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/menumodelsignalname\/itemschanged","abstract":[{"text":"Emitted when a change has occurred to the menu.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"MenuModelSignalName.itemsChanged","fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"itemsChanged","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","title":"GIO","url":"\/documentation\/gio","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/MenuModelSignalName":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MenuModelSignalName"}],"fragments":[{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"MenuModelSignalName"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MenuModelSignalName","abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/gio\/menumodelsignalname","role":"symbol","title":"MenuModelSignalName"}}}